<bioghist encodinganalog="545"><head>History of Xavier University Faculty Handbook Committee</head><p>On at least two occasions an ad hoc committee of faculty members and administrators was established to revise the Xavier faculty handbook. The first Faculty Handbook Committee met during the academic year 1966-67, resulting in the handbook that appeared in 1967. The second Faculty Handbook Committee for which we have records met from April 11, 1995 to April 8, 1998. Its work resulted in the 2000 handbook.</p><bioghist/></bioghist><scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a"><head>Scope and Content</head><p>This collection comprises editions of the Xavier University Faculty Handbook. Also included are the meeting minutes for two of the ad hoc committees formed to revise the handbook. Two publications used by one of the committees is also included.</p><scopecontent/></scopecontent><arrangement encodinganalog="351$b"><head>Statement of Arrangement</head><p>The bulk of the collection is arranged into faculty handbooks arranged chronologically and then by committee meeting minutes arranged chronologically.</p></arrangement><accessrestrict encodinganalog="506"><head>Restrictions on Access</head><p>Restricted access. Please contact the Xavier University archives staff.</p></accessrestrict><prefercite encodinganalog="524"><head>Preferred Citation</head><p>Box Number, Folder Number, XUA-28, Faculty Handbook collection, Special Collections and Archives, Xavier University Library, Cincinnati, Ohio.</p></prefercite><controlaccess><head>Indexing Terms</head><p>The following terms have been used to index the description of this collection in the library's online public access catalog.</p><controlaccess><head>Subjects:</head><subject encodinganalog="650$a" source="lcsh">Xavier University (Cincinnati, Ohio)--Faculty--Handbooks, manuals, etc.</subject></controlaccess><controlaccess><head>Organizations/Corporations:</head><corpname encodinganalog="710$a" source="lctgm">Xavier University (Cin